              Transform ideas into structured, prioritized backlogs. Say goodbye to weeks of meetings, 
              documentation, and planning — describe what you want to build and KodeOps handles the rest.
            </p>
            
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
