            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-500">
              Track progress against objectives with KPI dashboards and maintain 
              backlog health with automated prioritization and grooming.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-purple-50 rounded-xl p-6 opacity-75">
